The workshop brought together the multimedia community with the linguistic linked data community. The main topic was the analysis of cross-media usage of linguistic linked data within Italian public bodies and projects in private companies. A concrete outcome was the potential for a collaboration with the Chambers of Deputies for improving the publishing and  production of linked data and multimedia 
content.

